    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1887-04-11T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1887-04-11T00:00:00-05:00" n="11" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d11">
                <head>No. 11.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Quesada</persName> to Mr. <persName type="to">Bayard</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Argentine Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1887-04-11">
                            <hi rend="italic">April</hi> 11, 1887</date>.
                                (Received April 12.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to inform your excellency
                            that I have received instructions from the minister of foreign affairs
                            to communicate to your excellency, begging you to be so good as to lay
                            it before the President, the great satisfaction with which was received
                            the notice of your legation in the Argentine Republic being raised to
                            the rank of a first-class mission 5 since my Government sees in it a
                            proof of sympathy between the two nations, as well as a desire to
                            strengthen the relations which unite them on the basis of
                            reciprocity.</p>
                <p>In carrying out these instructions I avail myself, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Vicente G.
                            Quesada.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
